query: 如图,在△ABC中,BF平分∠ABC,AF⊥BF于点F,D为AB的中点,连接DF延长交AC于点E．若AB=10,BC=16,则线段EF的长为()选项：['2', '3', '4', '5']
answer: 解:∵AF⊥BF,∴∠AFB=90°,∵AB=10,D为AB中点,∴DF=\frac{1}{2}AB=AD=BD=5,∴∠ABF=∠BFD,又∵BF平分∠ABC,∴∠ABF=∠CBF,∴∠CBF=∠DFB,∴DE∥BC,∴△ADE∽△ABC,∴\frac{DE}{BC}=\frac{AD}{AB},即\frac{DE}{16}=\frac{5}{10},解得:DE=8,∴EF=DE-DF=3,故选:B．
